title: Un Juego Para Toda La Familia
description: After escaping London and a high-stress career, Justine plans to spend her days doing as little as possible in her Devon home. But soon after the move, her daughter Ellen starts to withdraw when her new best friend, George, is unfairly expelled from school. Justine begs the head teacher to reconsider, only to be told that nobody was expelled- George doesn't exist.
